.SH NOTICES
.PP
Note that transport protocol classes 0, 1, 2 and 3 are only available over a connection oriented
network service provider, such as
.BR cons (4).
Transport protocol class 4 is available over both connection oriented and connectionless underlying
networks,
.BR cons (4)
and
.BR clns (4),
and is used over the connectionless network protocol,
.BR clnp (4).
